dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Adams_Zoning_2015.gdb. The zoning feature layers included in this geodatabase are: 'COMP', and 'SHORELAND.'
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://adams-county-open-data-portal-adams-county-wi.hub.arcgis.com/
